    </a></p>
  </div>
  </li>
  <li><div class="panel">
    <h4 class="subheader">Društvo fizičara Srbije</h4>
    <p><a href="http://www.dfs.rs" >
      <img src="http://www.dfs.rs/images/dfs-logo.jpg" />
    </a></p>
  </div>
  </li>
